#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; is extremely ﬂexible and can be customized as much as you "
#| "like. You are able to change positions and size of all dock widgets next "
#| "to the central play area. You can also customize the toolbar if you want "
#| "to have diﬀerent actions accessible there. To do this just click on the "
#| "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu and choose <guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "toolbars...</guimenuitem>. The same is possible for all shortcuts in the "
#| "game. If you want to have the maximum space available for the game ﬁeld "
